Package: regNETcmap
Type: Package
Title: Tools to study transcriptional regulation using perturbation screens followed by transcriptomic profiling (incl. CMAP, Perturb-seq)
Version: 0.1.3
Author: Vitalii Kleshchevnikov
Maintainer: Vitalii Kleshchevnikov <vk7@sanger.ac.uk>
Description: This package provides tools to analyse CMAP data. Many functions are experimental as part of my ungoing research. Use with caution!
License: Apache 2.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: cmapR, data.table, rhdf5
Imports: downloader, biomaRt, UniProt.ws, clustermq, gsEasy, SingleCellExperiment, parallel, R.utils
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
